      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused BMW E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, offering precise shift throws and a direct mechanical connection. Key enthusiast-grade preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and structural subframe reinforcement to ensure long-term chassis integrity. The factory limited-slip differential provides consistent lock-up for optimal corner-exit traction. While the exterior displays minor road-derived patina, the mechanical vitals are strong, with linear power delivery and a well-sorted suspension utilizing upgraded bushings for sharpened turn-in response. A robust, mechanically honest specimen for the discerning purist.",
