      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between a well-loved daily driver and a meticulously maintained machine. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous finish, though a discerning eye will find the occasional minor stone chip on the hood and light surface swirling consistent with careful use. All body panels align perfectly, and the glass is crystal clear throughout. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the leather seats show only gentle softening on the driver's side bolster, and every electronic feature\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the premium audio system\u2014functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is robust. It has been serviced strictly on schedule, with a recent oil change and a multi-point inspection already completed. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. It drives straight, shifts smoothly, and offers the peace of mind that comes from a vehicle that has been genuinely cared for. Ready for its next owner with no immediate maintenance required.",
